# VPRAVA.ONLINE identity

This project’s product name and primary domain are **VPRAVA.ONLINE** (`https://vprava.online/`).

- Use **VPRAVA.ONLINE** in titles, About, PWA manifest, README, and user-facing copy.
- Use `vprava.online` in URLs and hostnames.
- Do not refer to the product as “Interval Training Timer” in new copy (legacy GitHub repo folder name may remain).
- Legacy host `timer.konashevych.com` may stay as a parallel URL; do not treat it as the primary brand.
- Drive vault folder id string `timer.konashevych.com` is intentional legacy — do not rename without a migration plan.
